    "name": "Wild West Pioneers",
    "steam_appid": 3222640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了拥挤的东海岸城市？带上家人前往西部，在这片自由的土地上开创属于你的未来。这里不仅有肥沃的土壤和丰富的资源，更充满了冒险与自由的无限可能。这是你能成为美国梦推动者的好时机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/1004c582489fb5f7187e4a300c888311.poster.avif?t=1771707757\" width=630 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/1004c582489fb5f7187e4a300c888311.webm?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/1004c582489fb5f7187e4a300c888311.mp4?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Wild West Pioneers》是一款融合了现代元素的经典城市建造游戏，让你亲手开发美国西部边陲。从零开始建设繁荣的定居点，选出城市领导者，建立食物、木材等生产链，满足居民的日常需求。随后派遣拓荒队进一步扩大你的势力范围。设立贸易路线，并为即将到来的铁路网做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/2cf7b1e2cb15176a83496505093a1d68.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Wild West Pioneer》的世界拥有丰富的任务、直观的操作界面和精美的视觉效果，完美再现了经典城市建造游戏的黄金时代，同时又赋予其现代化体验。在这里没有压力，只需一边休息，一边欣赏定居点的繁忙景象，看着数十种建筑和生产链有条不紊地运作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/11a1dca058c3f57272050e46db84ad48.poster.avif?t=1771707757\" width=630 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/11a1dca058c3f57272050e46db84ad48.webm?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/11a1dca058c3f57272050e46db84ad48.mp4?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/2cf7b1e2cb15176a83496505093a1d68.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/5eb1fef399bc1464d083710ef7e8194c.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >西部的模样由你来定。从居住房屋到商业建筑，你可以自由选择并建造，例如锯木厂、屠宰场、仓库和运输枢纽，确保物资的高效流通。随着定居者的需求不断变化，别忘了升级这些设施。你还可以任命市长和警长，但要慎重选择——他们的特性会影响城市发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/dd5ee269838df343c34ab79f81a945bc.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/5a7682a902aeeeb98503dec862fd361c.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立一个定居点只是开始。随着你发现新的资源流和生产链，扩张的需求会势不可挡。派遣定居者前往未知的土地，建立新的村庄。然后建立贸易路线，使资源能够被顺利交换。确保每个定居点都能良性发展，否则损失可能比想象中更严重。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/dd5ee269838df343c34ab79f81a945bc.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/452f2aec407de18e6462eae05a72d12b.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的村庄充满了性格各异的居民。他们都有自己的需求和期望，而你的任务就是满足他们，这样才能让你备受爱戴。定居者的幸福度受到就业机会、医疗条件等因素影响。只有当幸福度足够高，你才能吸引新的定居者加入，并成为推动美国西部扩张的重要力量。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/dd5ee269838df343c34ab79f81a945bc.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/6a3f5503c7233b05b5d03669d2a16559.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >昼夜循环会影响游戏世界的运作。看着城市从日出到日落不断变化，你需要展现真正的领导才能，合理规划生产链和贸易路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/dd5ee269838df343c34ab79f81a945bc.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/c3131328eb1d5ae78606c354479f7250.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >策略性地图将帮助你制定发展计划。派遣探险队，建立贸易前哨站，并组织车队让勇敢的拓荒者创建新定居点。在《Wild West Pioneers》的沙盒特性下，每一局游戏都会带来全新的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/dd5ee269838df343c34ab79f81a945bc.webp?t=1771707757\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/735a13a3c80623099836f7ab04b94727.webp?t=1771707757\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >坐下来，放松心情，欣赏你的计划一步步变成现实。观看城市的繁忙景象，每一份工作都由个性鲜明的人物完成，而不是简单的数据模拟。见证你的定居点一点点发展壮大，享受游戏的这一大乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/d1de4f160ee7d525bb763eb0bc35d793.poster.avif?t=1771707757\" width=630 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/d1de4f160ee7d525bb763eb0bc35d793.webm?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222640/extras/d1de4f160ee7d525bb763eb0bc35d793.mp4?t=1771707757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
